* Make file locale/kik.pot:

xgettext -d kik -p ./locale -o kik.pot -L Python *.py

* Cerate new transalate:

mkdir -p ll_CC/LC_MESSAGES
msginit -i locale/kik.pot -l ll_CC.UTF-8 -o ll_CC/LC_MESSAGES/kik.po

when ll_CC is locale name

* Merge existing file *.po:

msgmerge -U locale/pl_PL/LC_MESSAGES/kik.po locale/kik.pot

* Compile file kik.po to binary file kik.mo:

msgfmt locale/ll_CC/LC_MESSAGES/kik.po -o locale/ll_CC/LC_MESSAGES/kik.mo
